Lingering winter
We celebrated the new year, then January passed and it became February.
The world keeps moving on so fast that I cannot believe I left my house only a month and a half ago.
During that time, I tried to concentrate only on my work.
The most popular is probably Italian.
For Chinese food, the turntable...
In reality, work was the only thing I had.
In order not to think of unnecessary things...
But...
Hello!
Hi, we have been waiting for you.
I am sorry I was late.
Not at all.
It was not something so easily done.
Hey.
I will lend you taxi money, so...
Koshiro-san, it is cold.

Good morning!

I have thought about my feelings, your feelings, and many things since then.

Right?
Hey Nanoka.
What are you worried about?
You have not been looking too well recently.
Last time you said you would sleep over, but you suddenly went home.
Something seems wrong.
What is it?
Did something happen?
Nothing happened.
Do not worry.
You do not have to hide it!
If there is something making you suffer or troubling you,
you know you can tell me anything!
If there is anything I can do, I will help you!
I do not think you would understand, Futaba-chan.
Probably...
I am sorry.
What is that?
You will not tell me anything, so how am I supposed to understand?
But even if I think about it by myself,
I am not able to find an answer.
Please take care of me tonight too.
You know...
I do not mind you staying over, but what are you going to do about a change of clothes and stuff?
I will go home first and get them.
Then why do not you just sleep at your own home?
But your place is closer to the office,
so I will be able to sleep in more in the morning.
Jeez.
That is why I went to the front of my brother's office a couple of times and..
I also tried going to my brother's house.
But...
Let us promise.
Today is the last day.
We will not meet again.
I remember my brother's words and
I restrained myself.
Thank you for the food.
You are not going to eat any more?

Yeah, I am full.
But brother...
I cannot lie about my own feelings.
Brother, I still...
That idiot!
I told him to wake me up at six!
I slept in a weird position, so my whole body aches.
You slept over again?
Poor Koshiro-san.
Are you picking a fight with me?
If you keep on being his constant guest, he will not have any time to bring in girls!
I am a girl too!
Is that your reason for being his constant guest?
You think?
I wonder why?
What?
Why he suddenly started living on his own.
I am sure he has his reasons.
Like within his house.
Maybe he...!
Sniffed Nanoka-san's underwear and got disowned!

What kind of facial expression would they make, if I told them that was exactly the reason?
I sniffed her underwear, I thought of her and masturbated.
And in the end I embraced her.
I left my house in order to cut off that part of myself,
but I am just thinking about her anyway.
What would you think if you found out about this part of me?
Do not frown like that!
I did not intend to.
Everyone forgets things.
Yeah.
I will leave right after I find my pass.
I am not saying do not come.
I would be more considerate if you had a girlfriend or something.
Koshiro...
It is not like you are not interested in women, right?
Because I have not heard any romance rumours.
I was talking with Odagiri today too, but...
Ah, wait a second, I am going to go buy some cigarettes.
What is she saying?
Hey, is not that Nanoka-ch-
Ouch!
What is wrong with you?
Let go of me!
What is wrong?
What are you thinking?!
My hair got all messed up!
Hey!
Why do not you say something?
Why do we have to hide from Nanoka-chan?
She left!
Is it okay?
Why do you run away?
Hey, Koshiro?
Why are you running away?
Is Nanoka-chan the reason why you left your home, Koshiro?
Then...
Forget it.
I guess there are different kinds of household circumstances.
Odagiri was worried about you too.
He was saying maybe you sniffed your sister's underwear.
Or you surprised her while she was asleep.
He says those things so seriously, too.
I did not do anything!
Before those things happen...
Why are you getting all serious?
I was just kidding!
Come to think of it, you guys were not very sibling-like, to say...
You guys were spreading an odd atmosphere.
I guess you could not leave her alone, since she was so attached to you.
Nanoka-chan is so cute and everything.
Before too, she seemed to think of you more like a prince than a brother.
She made her eyes twinkle.
Did you make a move on her?
You...
What the hell are you thinking?!
She is your younger sister!
Without even thinking about the rest of her life!
You bastard!
I did not!
That is why I left before anything happened!
What is your problem?
You do not know anything!
Why do I have to take all this from you?
I did not know either, that at first, we were siblings...
That is sick.
It is disgusting.
Are you saying this for real?
Being so old.
Your younger sister... your blood related sister too.
The hell is that?
That is low.
You are a pervert.
That is right.
In the end, that is what it is.
I should have already known that long before, but...
But I...
It was the first time I felt this way.
That is why I want to see you, brother.
Good morning.
Where is Koshiro?
He is not coming since he is not feeling well.
He called in with a voice sounding like he was about to die.
Poor condition, huh?
Do you know something?
Yeah, it is really terrible.
So that is why you did not stay over last night?
It might not get better.
What?
That bad?
That coward.
Unfortunately, I was not able to get a comment from Kanako-san.
So that means it is not for sure yet.
Yes, that is true, but...
So it means she was just looking at a female magazine.
Yes.
Then she is not really able to give you any comment.
But I believe she could have given a little bit.
A little bit?
But if it really is marriage, then at this time of year it is a bit odd.
Not just limiting it to celebrities, do not you think so?
I do not know what to say.
I am sure you know these kinds of things better than I do.

I have heard such rumours, too.

Do we know the reason?

Anyway, it seems like a celebratory occasion.
Yes?
YOU-umm...

Unable to be resolved.
Unable to give up.
Running away from her and running away from work.
Forever with this incomplete emotion.
Putting a pitiful face on.
What am I?
I want to see you too...
